Package com.limuelle

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Command
    Command interface that contains an execute method which is implemented by concrete Command classes.
    Monster
    Monster interface containing methods which is implemented by concrete Monster classes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Game
    Contains the main method that runs the whole game.
    GameFunction
    Contains the rest of the game methods and game information.
    MonsterFactory
    Factory class that contains the method that generate object of concrete Monster class.
    Player
    Contains all of the player's attributes.
    RemoteControl
    The invoker class that contains the methods that can hold and execute a command as an object.
